### 1. GET Available Vehicles

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Vehicles?$filter=status eq 'Available'

### 2. GET Shipments filtered by status "InTransit"

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Shipments?$filter=status eq 'InTransit'

### 3. GET all shipments for a specific customer

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Shipments?$filter=customer_ID eq '5d463303-a4dd-6477-0ech-6358e789c002'

### 4. POST a new shipment booking

POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Shipments
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "trackingNumber": "SL-2026-00009",
    "customer_ID": "5f8d0c9e-1234-5678-90ab-cdef12345675",
    "pickupAddress": "123 Tech Park, Bengaluru",
    "deliveryAddress": "456 Business Road, Mumbai",
    "pickupCity": "Bengaluru",
    "deliveryCity": "Mumbai",
    "weight": 50,
    "status": "Booked",
    "deliveredAt": "2026-05-31T15:00:00Z"
}

### 5. PATCH shipment status to "Delivered" and set deliveredAt

PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Shipments(ID='7f685505-c6ff-8699-2gej-8570g901e001')
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "Delivered",
    "deliveredAt": "2026-05-31T20:00:00Z"
}

### 6. GET routes between two cities

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Routes?$filter=fromCity eq 'Bengaluru' and toCity eq 'Mumbai'

### 7. GET drivers sorted by rating descending

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/Logistics/Drivers?$orderby=rating desc
 